{"type": "article", "id": 15986, "title": "刀剪刀", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-13T06:10:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000335noIGyZjzfHswB60R.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套剪刀结合了日本武士刀的样式，来自刀具制造商 Nikken Cutlery。其中一款甚至以织田信长的佩刀压切为原型，剪刀的把手印有红色柄卷，呼应刀刃处缠绕的红绳，刀柄上还有织田家的家徽，以纪念最原始的武士精神。此外，Nikken Cutlery 还推出了一款黑色的架子，将剪刀倒立放置，完全是一个装饰品。<a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/s/ref=sr_pg_1?rh=i%3Aaps%2Ck%3A%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%80%E3%81%AF%E3%81%95%E3%81%BF&amp;keywords=%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%88%80%E3%81%AF%E3%81%95%E3%81%BF&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1443687518\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143421UDBtzeiF5RyHG1jf.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"493\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.85\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143422UzgEHdI8DAiL7NuW.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"694\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.19655172\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143422eqD932xuNtgdf0Mc.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"551\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.95\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143423kOmLDlqotrfgiGI5.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"753\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.255\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143423MrbNSPdUo5RlyWz1.jpg\" width=\"599\" height=\"569\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.94991653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}